Description:
   Disk's Word is a high-level Cleric offensive ability invoking the divine
   authority of Disk, the god of balance and judgment. The Cleric channels
   the full weight of Disk's judgment as a spoken divine decree, calling
   down retribution upon all enemies in the area. The spell deals massive
   holy damage to every enemy in the room.

   Disk's Word is the Cleric equivalent of a holy word — an area-effect
   divine blast that demonstrates the Cleric's role as a conduit for divine
   will rather than a mere healer. The spell does not discriminate between
   enemies; all hostile entities in the presence of the Cleric when the Word
   is spoken are struck. It represents the ultimate expression of Disk's
   impartial, all-encompassing judgment delivered through their faithful servant.
*******************************************************************************
